<p>The module changes colors, fonts, enables/disables some functionality. Moreover, it allows you to:</p>
<ul>
	<li>Enable/disable short description display in product lists;</li>
	<li>Change the symbols limits of the short description and product title;</li>
	<li>Unify the height of product lists (make sure you theme supports the feature)</li>
	<li>Choose if you want to display either 2 or 1 product in a row on mobile devices</li>
	<li>Add custom CSS/JS</li>
</ul>
<p>Press Configure to learn all the features.</p>